      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANGRY MURRAY COD (1) was out of the placings last time when fifth at Warragul (23.15) but scored five back at Ballarat (25.87). Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. ARCHIE MCIVOR (7) ran below best last time finishing fourth (19.43) over 350m at this track from Box 6. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Deserves plenty of respect. YEAH YOU (8) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.97) at Warragul behind Tilly Girl in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can feature again. FIDDLES (2) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.",
